N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 192.8 - Employment of dispensers

State Regulations

Prior to the dispensing of a hearing aid, a dispenser must
present a certificate of registration, either permanent or temporary, to a
prospective employer (business registrant). Notes
